1
00:00:05,170 --> 00:00:08,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}ONE MONTH EARLIER</font>

2
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:14,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you to do something 
about this, Captain.</font>

3
00:00:15,180 --> 00:00:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've seen those symptoms before.</font>

4
00:00:17,900 --> 00:00:19,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh...</font>

5
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:21,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happiness.</font>

6
00:00:22,150 --> 00:00:23,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I <i>knew</i> it.</font>

7
00:00:24,100 --> 00:00:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you been making 
time to see her lately?</font>

8
00:00:27,630 --> 00:00:28,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

9
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm... I guess we'll ask the guild 
for a quest as an excuse again</font>

10
00:00:32,470 --> 00:00:35,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and invite Happiness and 
Cecilia to go with us.</font>

11
00:00:35,160 --> 00:00:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh...</font>

12
00:00:36,290 --> 00:00:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could he not just invite 
her on a date like normal?</font>

13
00:00:40,160 --> 00:00:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}DATE?!</font>

14
00:00:40,340 --> 00:00:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A d-date?!</font>

15
00:00:43,540 --> 00:00:47,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have two superiors who can't even 
ask the girls they like on a date.</font>

16
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My life <i>sucks</i>.</font>

17
00:00:49,770 --> 00:00:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay!</font>

18
00:00:52,730 --> 00:00:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Operation Go on a Group Date as 
a Drastic Measure to Help Raven...</font>

19
00:00:56,650 --> 00:00:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is underway!</font>

20
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sunny day.</font>

21
00:02:33,490 --> 00:02:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't the weather just lovely?</font>

22
00:02:35,710 --> 00:02:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do our best to 
have lots of fun today!</font>

23
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:42,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Duke, since when were 
you and Irene a thing?</font>

24
00:02:42,940 --> 00:02:46,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I said we were giving 
the captain a break,</font>

25
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:48,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she said she wanted to help.</font>

26
00:02:46,380 --> 00:02:50,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm so excited! I hope we 
find something good to eat!</font>

27
00:02:50,170 --> 00:02:52,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, we're heading out now.</font>

28
00:02:53,610 --> 00:02:56,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So where are we headed, anyway?</font>

29
00:02:56,410 --> 00:02:58,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's someplace Happiness wants to go.</font>

30
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're starting with that.</font>

31
00:03:00,610 --> 00:03:01,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dying to.</font>

32
00:03:01,130 --> 00:03:02,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}WHERE?</font>

33
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you mean the famous spot 
that just opened recently?</font>

34
00:03:05,330 --> 00:03:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You nailed it.</font>

35
00:03:06,850 --> 00:03:10,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A famous spot that just 
opened? You don't mean...</font>

36
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:17,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}LET'S GO TO A BAKERY.</font>

37
00:03:16,050 --> 00:03:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Refuse.</font>

38
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}LET'S GET LUNCH!</font>

39
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too early.</font>

40
00:03:28,530 --> 00:03:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That place will probably be crowded,</font>

41
00:03:30,490 --> 00:03:33,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and if we go there, it 
could lead to chaos.</font>

42
00:03:33,910 --> 00:03:35,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's not do that today.</font>

43
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Break free!</font>

44
00:03:48,410 --> 00:03:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow...</font>

45
00:03:50,490 --> 00:03:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This looks amazing!</font>

46
00:03:53,010 --> 00:03:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The king made it to celebrate 
the Demon King's defeat.</font>

47
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Identical.</font>

48
00:04:00,570 --> 00:04:03,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}PLEASE DON'T LOOK.</font>

49
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be modest.</font>

50
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm proud.</font>

51
00:04:18,370 --> 00:04:20,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like it's going well.</font>

52
00:04:20,430 --> 00:04:22,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The plan's clearly a success.</font>

53
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happiness, you have cream on your cheek.</font>

54
00:04:27,250 --> 00:04:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain?</font>

55
00:04:31,710 --> 00:04:33,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It <i>is</i> the captain.</font>

56
00:04:33,660 --> 00:04:36,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that voice we just heard...</font>

57
00:04:36,030 --> 00:04:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

58
00:04:38,700 --> 00:04:41,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So sorry.</font>

59
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:44,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the first time 
we've heard your voice,</font>

60
00:04:44,250 --> 00:04:47,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we were a bit surprised.</font>

61
00:04:51,610 --> 00:04:52,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rude!</font>

62
00:04:54,150 --> 00:04:56,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vice Captain, good to see you.</font>

63
00:04:56,870 --> 00:04:59,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The captain's off duty today,</font>

64
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:02,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so don't worry about him. You 
can continue your patrol.</font>

65
00:05:02,030 --> 00:05:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hah! He has not only his subordinate, 
but a fragile girl defending him?</font>

66
00:05:08,550 --> 00:05:11,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, go ahead and enjoy your day off,</font>

67
00:05:11,550 --> 00:05:13,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Sir Raven."</font>

68
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Captain?</font>

69
00:05:22,130 --> 00:05:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raven...</font>

70
00:05:29,550 --> 00:05:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Raven!</font>

71
00:05:31,130 --> 00:05:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll bring him right back!</font>

72
00:05:32,690 --> 00:05:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go with you!</font>

73
00:05:37,130 --> 00:05:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't blame him for being shocked, 
but I didn't think he'd run away.</font>

74
00:05:41,010 --> 00:05:45,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There were always some knights who didn't 
like having a captain who didn't talk.</font>

75
00:05:45,110 --> 00:05:49,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was the vice captain who brought 
them all together as a faction.</font>

76
00:05:50,290 --> 00:05:51,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still a rookie,</font>

77
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so there's only so much I 
can do to stick up for him.</font>

78
00:05:55,170 --> 00:05:57,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got it harder than I thought.</font>

79
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:00,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over there!</font>

80
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:06,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This game of tag is over.</font>

81
00:06:06,250 --> 00:06:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's head back to the others.</font>

82
00:06:08,450 --> 00:06:10,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going to happen if I go back?</font>

83
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:11,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

84
00:06:12,250 --> 00:06:15,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're running away because 
you got embarrassed?</font>

85
00:06:15,110 --> 00:06:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you never want to see 
Happiness again, then?</font>

86
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:19,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

87
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:23,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I was fine with it 
as long as Happiness was happy.</font>

88
00:06:23,470 --> 00:06:24,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a letdown.</font>

89
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you still insist on keeping 
silent, I guess it is what it is.</font>

90
00:06:30,540 --> 00:06:32,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's all yours from here.</font>

91
00:06:36,570 --> 00:06:38,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's really wrong?</font>

92
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:43,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lately, I've been reminded of 
my own weakness and powerlessness.</font>

93
00:06:44,170 --> 00:06:46,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You remember that quest 
we did at the ocean?</font>

94
00:06:47,910 --> 00:06:52,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">That day, Happiness told 
me she had a secret.</font></font>

95
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:56,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She seemed to be afraid of something,</font>

96
00:06:56,890 --> 00:06:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so it must be a really big deal.</font>

97
00:07:01,130 --> 00:07:04,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But how can I accept 
whatever her secret is</font>

98
00:07:05,330 --> 00:07:08,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when all I ever do is worry and fret?</font>

99
00:07:09,130 --> 00:07:10,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the same with my voice.</font>

100
00:07:11,940 --> 00:07:13,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I've done is run from it.</font>

101
00:07:14,290 --> 00:07:15,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If only I could</font>

102
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:19,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">have the courage to approach 
the girl I love, like you do...</font>

103
00:07:19,780 --> 00:07:20,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say what?!</font>

104
00:07:21,890 --> 00:07:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just who do you think I am?</font>

105
00:07:24,770 --> 00:07:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went out alone with the girl I love,</font>

106
00:07:27,030 --> 00:07:30,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'm such a shy loser, I had 
to wear a mask the whole time!</font>

107
00:07:30,550 --> 00:07:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On your feet, Raven!</font>

108
00:07:33,050 --> 00:07:36,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those legs aren't just for 
show, are they?! Hell no!</font>

109
00:07:36,820 --> 00:07:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you're not that weak!</font>

110
00:07:39,690 --> 00:07:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do I know?</font>

111
00:07:40,810 --> 00:07:42,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I, like Duke and Happiness,</font>

112
00:07:43,190 --> 00:07:45,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">have faith in you!</font>

113
00:07:47,730 --> 00:07:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That bizarre mood you create 
always cheers me up somehow.</font>

114
00:07:56,750 --> 00:07:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, everyone.</font>

115
00:08:03,060 --> 00:08:05,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I acted selfishly.</font>

116
00:08:07,290 --> 00:08:08,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forgiven.</font>

117
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, now that the captain's 
game of tag is over,</font>

118
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we're going shopping next!</font>

119
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait!</font>

120
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happiness...</font>

121
00:08:27,130 --> 00:08:29,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you can't rely on me now,</font>

122
00:08:29,610 --> 00:08:32,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'll try harder so you can 
entrust me with your secret one day.</font>

123
00:08:34,670 --> 00:08:35,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Acknowledged.</font>

124
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:40,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}A FEW DAYS LATER</font>

125
00:08:39,380 --> 00:08:40,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yoki!</font>

126
00:08:42,210 --> 00:08:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Cecilia?</font>

127
00:08:44,700 --> 00:08:47,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happiness has gone missing!</font>

128
00:08:47,550 --> 00:08:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

129
00:08:49,380 --> 00:08:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happiness did put in a 
request for extended leave,</font>

130
00:08:54,290 --> 00:08:56,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but this note she wrote is so puzzling...</font>

131
00:08:58,590 --> 00:09:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep, it's written the way she talks.</font>

132
00:09:01,820 --> 00:09:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does it mean?</font>

133
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}ONE MONTH 
COME FIND 
FOREST</font>

134
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It says, "Come find me in 
the forest in one month."</font>

135
00:09:07,860 --> 00:09:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What forest is she talking about?</font>

136
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:13,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I might know.</font>

137
00:09:13,950 --> 00:09:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happiness must have something in mind.</font>

138
00:09:22,540 --> 00:09:24,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happy!</font>

139
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hi.</font>

140
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, don't make me track you down 
with my enhanced sense of smell.</font>

141
00:09:31,170 --> 00:09:32,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trust.</font>

142
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:34,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone's worried about you, y'know.</font>

143
00:09:35,010 --> 00:09:38,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've made up my mind, so...</font>

144
00:09:38,970 --> 00:09:41,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to tell him...</font>

145
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:44,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">about me.</font>

146
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:46,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're sure?</font>

147
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:52,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Raven doesn't accept it, 
you could lose everything.</font>

148
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:54,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

149
00:09:54,860 --> 00:09:59,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They might want to investigate your 
relationship to us and the captain, too.</font>

150
00:10:00,140 --> 00:10:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that happens...</font>

151
00:10:01,560 --> 00:10:03,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't cause trouble.</font>

152
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:06,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This goes way beyond just causing trouble.</font>

153
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:08,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, Shiek, the captain...</font>

154
00:10:08,930 --> 00:10:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We could all lose everything we've 
gained since coming to Minerva.</font>

155
00:10:14,230 --> 00:10:16,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then again, you're smart,</font>

156
00:10:17,060 --> 00:10:18,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm sure you know all that.</font>

157
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't lie anymore.</font>

158
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:23,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want him to know.</font>

159
00:10:29,270 --> 00:10:30,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do this, Happy!</font>

160
00:10:30,890 --> 00:10:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiek...</font>

161
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:36,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is really important to you, right?</font>

162
00:10:36,010 --> 00:10:38,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'll be rooting for you!</font>

163
00:10:38,830 --> 00:10:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You feel the same, right, Duke?</font>

164
00:10:41,460 --> 00:10:42,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

165
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that's how strong your resolve is,</font>

166
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">don't worry about us. Just go and do it.</font>

167
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:50,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

168
00:10:51,260 --> 00:10:53,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gotta say something too, Captain!</font>

169
00:10:53,570 --> 00:10:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you guys summed it 
all up so nicely for me.</font>

170
00:10:58,490 --> 00:11:00,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have nothing to add.</font>

171
00:11:00,090 --> 00:11:01,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Useless.</font>

172
00:11:02,890 --> 00:11:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kidding. Captain...</font>

173
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

174
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:20,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if it isn't Sir Raven. 
How are you feeling today?</font>

175
00:11:21,250 --> 00:11:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel just fine.</font>

176
00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:25,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That voice...</font>

177
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're being rude!</font>

178
00:11:27,910 --> 00:11:29,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you call me by name?</font>

179
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

180
00:11:31,210 --> 00:11:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not such a fool</font>

181
00:11:33,530 --> 00:11:37,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as to let a knight who disrupts 
the order with his lack of manners</font>

182
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">serve as vice captain.</font>

183
00:11:40,620 --> 00:11:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What do you mean by that, Sir Raven?</font>

184
00:11:44,780 --> 00:11:46,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will call me "Captain."</font>

185
00:11:54,410 --> 00:11:57,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My apologies, Captain.</font>

186
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:00,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THAT'S BETTER.</font>

187
00:12:08,100 --> 00:12:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}ONE MONTH LATER</font>

188
00:12:11,620 --> 00:12:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been just about a month 
now since Happiness went away.</font>

189
00:12:16,870 --> 00:12:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think she's going to...</font>

190
00:12:20,010 --> 00:12:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's exactly what you're imagining.</font>

191
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:27,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Duke should be taking Raven to 
where Happiness is as we speak.</font>

192
00:12:31,630 --> 00:12:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't realize that Yoki was here.</font>

193
00:12:33,540 --> 00:12:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother...</font>

194
00:12:34,940 --> 00:12:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You told him about your marriage 
arrangement, didn't you?</font>

195
00:12:38,180 --> 00:12:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

196
00:12:39,300 --> 00:12:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

197
00:12:40,180 --> 00:12:43,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has his hands full dealing 
with his friends right now.</font>

198
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:46,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to give him 
more to worry about.</font>

199
00:12:46,780 --> 00:12:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure? Your future husband 
has already arrived in Minerva.</font>

200
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki is going to find out eventually.</font>

201
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only agreed to meet him 
per the king's order.</font>

202
00:12:57,200 --> 00:13:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once I meet him, I'll turn 
down the offer right away.</font>

203
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me, Cecilia...</font>

204
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:08,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you really feel about Yoki?</font>

205
00:13:08,190 --> 00:13:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki has nothing to do with anything!</font>

206
00:13:11,690 --> 00:13:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, please don't tell him 
about that without my permission!</font>

207
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm... So you do feel <i>something</i> after all.</font>

208
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:22,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're wrong! I just...</font>

209
00:13:22,470 --> 00:13:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Silly.</font>

210
00:13:24,570 --> 00:13:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he really had nothing 
to do with anything,</font>

211
00:13:26,570 --> 00:13:30,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you wouldn't want to keep your marriage 
arrangement a secret from him.</font>

212
00:13:51,910 --> 00:13:54,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is... Happiness's...</font>

213
00:13:55,070 --> 00:13:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come with me.</font>

214
00:14:01,380 --> 00:14:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is Happiness?</font>

215
00:14:06,410 --> 00:14:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki, I have to kill you.</font>

216
00:14:09,610 --> 00:14:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought if anyone could accept 
her, it'd be you. What a letdown.</font>

217
00:14:13,620 --> 00:14:15,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could say the same about you.</font>

218
00:14:16,870 --> 00:14:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not seriously...</font>

219
00:14:18,870 --> 00:14:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is nothing to discuss!</font>

220
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Explain what's going on!</font>

221
00:14:28,850 --> 00:14:32,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm punishing you for hurting 
Happiness! Steel yourself!</font>

222
00:14:32,590 --> 00:14:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

223
00:14:37,390 --> 00:14:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said wait!</font>

224
00:14:49,790 --> 00:14:50,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

225
00:14:54,710 --> 00:14:56,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's stronger than before?!</font>

226
00:15:14,870 --> 00:15:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's your true identity,</font>

227
00:15:17,700 --> 00:15:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki.</font>

228
00:15:19,310 --> 00:15:22,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you do to Happiness, Raven?</font>

229
00:15:24,230 --> 00:15:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need to tell you!</font>

230
00:15:28,610 --> 00:15:30,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is...</font>

231
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">enough!</font>

232
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:35,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Endless Dark!</font>

233
00:15:47,500 --> 00:15:51,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you get it now, Raven? 
You can't beat me.</font>

234
00:15:52,690 --> 00:15:54,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I won't give up!</font>

235
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you so determined?</font>

236
00:15:56,950 --> 00:15:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened between you and Happiness?</font>

237
00:15:59,710 --> 00:16:01,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promised her.</font>

238
00:16:01,590 --> 00:16:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said you plucked every feather from 
her body to disguise her as a human,</font>

239
00:16:05,830 --> 00:16:08,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and she asked me to give 
you a beating for it.</font>

240
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha?</font>

241
00:16:10,780 --> 00:16:11,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

242
00:16:12,060 --> 00:16:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what's going on. So let's do this.</font>

243
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me a <i>break</i>!</font>

244
00:16:16,290 --> 00:16:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you give me a beating with 
that sword, even I'm gonna die!</font>

245
00:16:20,020 --> 00:16:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... Well, then, I'll just...</font>

246
00:16:22,950 --> 00:16:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">use the back edge.</font>

247
00:16:24,830 --> 00:16:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sword's double-edged!</font>

248
00:16:36,690 --> 00:16:39,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happiness!</font>

249
00:16:42,550 --> 00:16:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doot do-doo!</font>

250
00:16:45,540 --> 00:16:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A mischievous spirit can 
only take you so far!</font>

251
00:16:53,070 --> 00:16:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apology.</font>

252
00:16:54,530 --> 00:16:55,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

253
00:16:57,180 --> 00:17:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And? How did you two... 
well... settle things?</font>

254
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:04,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, well...</font>

255
00:17:04,080 --> 00:17:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Duke led me to a certain forest, and...</font>

256
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll have to go on your own from here.</font>

257
00:17:12,340 --> 00:17:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Duke?</font>

258
00:17:14,050 --> 00:17:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're gonna have to give 
Happiness an answer yourself.</font>

259
00:17:22,840 --> 00:17:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happiness?</font>

260
00:17:27,080 --> 00:17:29,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happiness, are you up there?</font>

261
00:17:30,130 --> 00:17:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why... are you hiding?</font>

262
00:17:32,890 --> 00:17:34,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Visitor. Gratitude.</font>

263
00:17:35,460 --> 00:17:37,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you want me to come here?</font>

264
00:17:38,360 --> 00:17:39,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

265
00:17:40,550 --> 00:17:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">where I started.</font>

266
00:17:43,270 --> 00:17:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And... where I ended.</font>

267
00:17:49,670 --> 00:17:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's a place that means a lot to you.</font>

268
00:17:53,550 --> 00:17:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raven, I'm glad I met you.</font>

269
00:17:56,540 --> 00:17:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spending time with you is fun.</font>

270
00:17:58,790 --> 00:18:00,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to be together forever.</font>

271
00:18:01,110 --> 00:18:01,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I also—</font>

272
00:18:01,930 --> 00:18:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! Don't come closer!</font>

273
00:18:25,770 --> 00:18:27,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was scared.</font>

274
00:18:27,410 --> 00:18:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't keep lying forever.</font>

275
00:18:30,170 --> 00:18:36,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... when I thought... 
it might mean the end...</font>

276
00:18:41,690 --> 00:18:42,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

277
00:18:50,250 --> 00:18:51,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raven?</font>

278
00:18:52,730 --> 00:18:55,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I didn't notice.</font>

279
00:18:56,630 --> 00:18:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been suffering 
over this for so long.</font>

280
00:18:59,540 --> 00:19:01,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't reject me?</font>

281
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:06,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not. Because I love you.</font>

282
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that's not a 
sufficient reason, is it?</font>

283
00:19:08,670 --> 00:19:10,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I...</font>

284
00:19:12,620 --> 00:19:13,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">love you, too.</font>

285
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:18,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then everything's fine, right?</font>

286
00:19:18,910 --> 00:19:19,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

287
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:30,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so <i>sweet</i>!</font>

288
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's way too sweet!</font>

289
00:19:32,380 --> 00:19:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sweeter than the sugar 
cubes at Cecilia's house!</font>

290
00:19:37,730 --> 00:19:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two had a fairy-tale ending like that,</font>

291
00:19:41,130 --> 00:19:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you were talking about beating me up?!</font>

292
00:19:44,040 --> 00:19:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. I get it.</font>

293
00:19:47,030 --> 00:19:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me offer you my congratulations.</font>

294
00:19:50,750 --> 00:19:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saint Chains!</font>

295
00:19:52,500 --> 00:19:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this for?!</font>

296
00:19:53,890 --> 00:19:54,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Undo!</font>

297
00:19:55,040 --> 00:19:57,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! I'll put up a barrier 
to keep monsters out.</font>

298
00:19:58,180 --> 00:20:00,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you two have a nice time now!</font>

299
00:20:06,950 --> 00:20:08,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a relief.</font>

300
00:20:09,170 --> 00:20:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If, by some chance, Raven and 
Happiness didn't work out,</font>

301
00:20:12,100 --> 00:20:14,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we probably couldn't have tea 
together like this anymore.</font>

302
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia?</font>

303
00:20:17,560 --> 00:20:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm sorry!</font>

304
00:20:21,210 --> 00:20:25,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... I'm going to be a 
little busy for a while,</font>

305
00:20:25,270 --> 00:20:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I won't have much time for tea.</font>

306
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but it's only for a little while!</font>

307
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:32,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, okay. Don't worry about it.</font>

308
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be away from Minerva for a while.</font>

309
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:35,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

310
00:20:35,930 --> 00:20:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuga asked me to help him with a quest,</font>

311
00:20:39,820 --> 00:20:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I have to go to some mine somewhere.</font>

312
00:20:42,710 --> 00:20:44,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... see...</font>

313
00:20:47,220 --> 00:20:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He kind of begged me.</font>

314
00:20:49,930 --> 00:20:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might take two or three weeks.</font>

315
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:57,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So at some point, you became 
good friends with Yuga, too?</font>

316
00:20:57,240 --> 00:20:57,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

317
00:20:59,420 --> 00:21:00,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Yoki here?!</font>

318
00:21:02,190 --> 00:21:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give Yoki to us.</font>

319
00:21:04,830 --> 00:21:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apprehend! Haul in!</font>

320
00:21:06,890 --> 00:21:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki, did you do something again?</font>

321
00:21:11,340 --> 00:21:14,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They messed with me first!</font>

322
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:17,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for the tea!</font>

323
00:21:21,250 --> 00:21:22,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll come by again!</font>

324
00:21:25,220 --> 00:21:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you run away!</font>

325
00:21:26,220 --> 00:21:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Annihilate!</font>

326
00:21:27,780 --> 00:21:30,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly... You'd better.</font>

327
00:21:32,710 --> 00:21:34,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, too.</font>

328
00:22:00,060 --> 00:22:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happiness! I'm happy for you!</font>

329
00:22:02,450 --> 00:22:04,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations!</font>

330
00:22:07,780 --> 00:22:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems we have a debt to 
Yoki that we can never repay.</font>

331
00:22:11,090 --> 00:22:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Captain.</font>

